#{290}{}{So we've got you to thank for the caravan, huh? Did you even think about what'll happen to Black Rock, now? They'll bring more people here. Whores, drug addicts, criminals. You don't even give a shit, do you? You don't even live here. You're just some stranger who blew in from the wastes, and you've decided all of our futures. How fucked up is that?}
